                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#33vb">f. 33vb</locus>: Ownership note extended by an exhortation to the community.<quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="33vb">33vb</locus>: ዝመጽሐፈ፡ ጥምቀት፡ ዘመስጥሕ፡ ዘአባ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ዘአጽሐፍዋ፡ አቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ ተንሣኤ፡ ወቄስ፡ ገበዝ፡ አቡነ፡ ቄስ፡ ኢዮአብ፡ ምነው፡ አባቶቼ፡ ወንድሞቼ፡ በምን፡ ነገር፡ ትጠሉኝ፡ አላቹህ፡ አሁን፡ አንድ፡ ቁምነገር፡ ሳልሰራ፡ አልቀርም፡ አትጥሉኝ።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written partly in Gǝʿǝz and Amharic, possibly by the same hand as the main text. The note mentions that the Ms. is owned by the church of Libānos of Mäsṭǝḥ (cp. Additio 1 in MR-041 and MR-037). It mentions also the name of the commissioners of the Ms., <roleName type="title">ʾabuna</roleName> Walda Tänśaʾe and <roleName type="title">qes gabaz</roleName> ʾIyoʾab.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#34r">f. 34r</locus>: Excerpt from a liturgical hymn (unidentified).<quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="34r">34r</locus>: አርያም፡ ቀዳሜ፡ ዜማ። ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለአብ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለወልድ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። ዮሐንስኒ፡ ሀሎ፡ ያጠምቅ፡ በሄኖን፡ በቅሩበ፡ ስሌም፡ በማዕዶተ፡ ዮርዳኖስ፡ ወብርሃነ፡ ጽድቅሰ፡ ውእቱ፡ ኢያሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ።</quote>
